{"tid":1542980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「推上熱門」台灣有需要流亡人士請入","createTime":"2019-09-05T04:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T09:33:00.000Z","uid":243348,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"36f983fa93d8dc8b4ff63182a3450d2625650de7","tid":1542980,"uid":243348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:32:16.000Z","msg":"借ac <br />\n細佬見到個po關於 去左台灣嘅義士需要幫手<br />\n而咁啱細佬係台灣讀書 自己租屋 任你住<br />\n錢唔多 供到一段時間 主要係短期援助<br />\n我日日見到香港大佬們 幫手擋棍 檔子彈 自己咩都做唔到<br />\n所以想幫下義士<br />\n唔該大家幫我推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">為加快進度， 麻煩按照下列步驟聯絡我<br />\n<br />\n1. 將入台證用物理方式遮去個人資料<br />\n<br />\n2. 附上手寫連登id影相寄去以下tg，需留意入台證相片要影到入境日期同出境期限<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/sphey\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsphey&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruUcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=78bfd7d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/sphey</a><br />\n<br />\n2-1. 無連登帳號嘅義士可只寄入台證 但會問返幾個問題 <br />\n<br />\n*審核過程有機會要求其他能證明身份之文件 如 學生證。<br />\n文件上記之敏感個人資料請以物理方式遮蔽。<br />\n<br />\n3. 人工資料審核通過後將會轉介比 我要買MTR 巴打討論如何對閣下予以協助</span><br />\n<br />\n以上程序由另一位師兄幫手進行 主要係保障返我嘅安全<br />\n而你亦可以用你嘅方式去驗證我嘅身份 <br />\n<br />\n而如果有其他需要都可以聯絡下 幫到盡幫<br />\n<br />\n兄弟們唔洗怕羞 有需要盡量出聲"},{"pid":"d60c33fe380a4cc20833b61f44af6bde479501db","tid":1542980,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:32:38.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5EAUpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5EAUpQ.jpg&h=30bf1600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UUE1PYa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUUE1PYa.jpg&h=d8331036&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1sNZBDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1sNZBDb.jpg&h=ace5c24e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8KM7Lwx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8KM7Lwx.jpg&h=5719ebc4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoyFk4T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoyFk4T.jpg&h=2bffae59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SsV05wz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSsV05wz.jpg&h=d54e941c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EUH604U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEUH604U.jpg&h=74590733&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0744bcac518dd6d3196bf5421952785e41f1df80","tid":1542980,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"[831太子] 係咪要義士死得不明不白？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542890\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542890</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3c54a071af2bfb814ac854573f0f0cab07b76e31","tid":1542980,"uid":243348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:33:13.000Z","msg":"10連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b179a0072898d4dab4009a01aa0ad20799c1b4bc","tid":1542980,"uid":243348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:33:23.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"b6f8b501f519c665cc2f085c2616f3ed972042c4","tid":1542980,"uid":243348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:33:33.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"24f2aaa869306e70771de3815ff246907cd46b6c","tid":1542980,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-0